reviewText: I bought season 1,2 and 3 and they are funny.they will work on English dvd player/blu ray players. The show reminds me of an 80s cartoon show. It's one of the best adult swim cartoon. I haven't seen the rest of adult swum cartoons but to me this is the best.
Title: Superjail: Season 2

reviewText: I don't understand how people can give this such a low score.  The animation, humor, and style are all in-tact here.  If I hadn't been told that this was written by different people, I wouldn't have been able to tell.  If you're a fan of the show, then do yourself a favor and pick this up.Bring on Season 3!
summary: A great follow up to the first season.
Title: Superjail: Season 2

reviewText: Not many folks like the 2nd season, but after I watched it for a second time, I realized that Season 2 was still pretty cool.The art style definitely changed, the crazy Superjail! melee's may have been reduced, but it was for the better !A more developed storyline was necessary for the show to continue on without it maintaining it's very erratic progression in story telling.It was for the better !
Title: Superjail: Season 2
